text: Haan unn per bhi koi haraj nahi jo aap kay pass aatay hain kay aap unhen sawari mohiyya ker den to aap jawab detay hain kay mein to tumahri sawari kay liye kuch bhi nahi pata to woh ranj-o-ghum say apni aakhon say aansoo bahatay huye lot jatay hain kay enhen kharach kerney kay liye kuch bhi mayyasar nahi
